comments: Joseph (SAC) establishes himself in a legal picking position in DeRozan's (SAS) path.
Aldridge (SAS) establishes himself in a picking position in Barnes' (SAC) path and makes marginal contact with Barnes as he slightly turns his body.
Ariza (SAC) does not establish himself in a legal defensive position and delivers contact to Murray's (SAS) body during his driving shot attempt.  Hield (SAC) is incorrectly called for the foul.
Murray (SAS) makes clean contact with the ball.
Mills (SAS) makes clean contact with the ball.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Murray's (SAS) path.
Hield (SAC) establishes himself in a legal screening position in DeRozan's (SAS) path.
Prior to the dribble, DeRozan (SAS) reaches in but does not make any illegal contact with Barnes (SAC) in the post.
Barnes (SAC) places a stayed forearm to DeRozan (SAS) prior to his upward shooting motion and the contact does not affect his trajectory or driving shot attempt.
Aldridge (SAS) engages with Holmes (SAC) during rebounding but does not dislodge him from his position.
Ariza (SAC) makes marginal contact to Aldridge's (SAS) arm that does not affect his shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul on Barnes (SAC) pursuant to a coach's challenge is deemed unsuccessful.  Barnes is late establishing himself in a picking position in Mills' (SAS) path and he delivers contact.
Holmes (SAC) jumps from point A to point B into Aldridge (SAS) that affects his shot attempt.  Hield (SAC) makes legal hand on ball contact.
Mills (SAS) commits a take foul on Joseph (SAC).
Mills (SAS) reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball during Hield's (SAC) drive.
Mills (SAS) makes marginal contact with Hield (SAC) but does not affect his ability to get to the inbound pass.
DeRozan (SAC) makes contact with the ball as Hield (SAC) rips through to pass.
Replay review of the foul on Mills (SAS) pursuant to a coach's challenge is deemed successful.  Mills makes clean contact with the ball and legally deflects it away from Ariza (SAC).
Walker IV (SAS) makes contact to Barnes' (SAC) arm.
Ariza (SAC) makes marginal contact with DeRozan's (SAS) arm on the rip-through.
Aldridge (SAS) legally firms up in Hield's (SAC) path during the screen.
Mills (SAS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Barnes (SAC) path.
Hield (SAC) makes contact with DeRozan's (SAS) upper body during the drive and affects his SQBR.
Aldridge (SAS) briefly places an arm to Barnes' (SAC) front during the pick.
DeRozan (SAS) gathers the ball and comes to a stop on two feet, and then slides both feet forward prior to releasing the pass.
Aldridge (SAS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Ariza's (SAC) path.
Ariza (SAC) makes marginal contact with Murray (SAS) at the end of the drive during the pass.
Joseph (SAC) jumps A to B and makes contact with Mills (SAS) after the release that affects his ability to land.
Mills (SAS) makes marginal contact with Hield (SAC) as they engage and disengage off-ball.
Hield (SAC) initiates marginal contact with Mills (SAS) during the drive.
Aldridge (SAS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Ariza's (SAC) path.
Hield (SAC) makes marginal contact while his arm is extended with Mills's (SAS) arm .  Mills's reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Holmes (SAC) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it from Aldridge (SAS) during the rebound.
After making clean contact with the ball, Mills (SAS) makes marginal contact with Hield's (SAC) body.
Hield (SAC) disengages from the contact and does not dislodge DeRozan (SAS) from his rebounding position.
